name: Ability, Ability, Ability
Lore: '''Ben. . . Ben, please! Ben. . . Leia! Hear me, Leia!''',
Text: 'Deploy on opponent''s side of table. At the end of opponent''s deploy phase, if they did not deploy a card with ability, opponent loses 2 Force. Effect lost if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you. (Immune to Alter.)',
